          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target used was natSn, which was prepared by",
                "rolling. The stack  was formed by positioning the",
                "aluminum foils immediately after the Sn  target foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Al foils were used as energy degraders and",
                "also as catcher  foils. Al-catcher foil thickness was",
                "chosen to stop all the recoiling evaporation  residues.",
                "In the stack, there were five target-catcher",
                "combinations each consisting of nat.Sn target of",
                "thickness 2.2 mg/cm2 and Al-foil of",
                "thickness 2.1 mg/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
